title: AW: Jennifer Hawkins Just Gave Birth To Her 1st Child, Frankie Violet
text:
Jennifer Hawkins and husband Jake Wall have welcomed their first child, Frankie Violet Hawkins Wall, into the world. My heart, it bursts with love.

Jen took to Instagram to announce the beautiful moment. “Dream come true!” she captioned the images. “So thankful to be holding our beautiful healthy baby girl! We couldn’t be more in love.”

READ MORE Jennifer Hawkins Announces She's Up The Duff And Expecting A Baby Girl

I mean, look at these images and try not to gush. Honestly.

The pair had announced the pregnancy back in May.

Earlier this year, Jen spoke with Stellar Magazine about her past troubles to fall pregnant since marrying Jake in 2013, including a miscarriage and an endometriosis diagnosis.

“Just to see a bump is like no other feeling when you’ve wanted it for so long,” Jen told the magazine, about her pregnancy with Frankie. “I don’t care if I put on weight or get stretch marks – the only thing I can think about is her being healthy.”

Congrats to Jen, Jake and the healthy bub. Thank you for making me clucky.
description: Jennifer Hawkins and Jake Wall have welcomed their first child, baby Frankie Violet, into the world. Jen took to Instagram to announce the beautiful moment.
